1. *Vojsci* se pridružio tokom ratnih dejstava. (He joined the army during the war operations.)
2. On se školovao za *vojscu*. (He was educated for the army.)
3. On je služio u *vojsci*. (He served in the army.)
4. *Vojsci* su potrebne nove uniforme. (The army needs new uniforms.)
5. On je bio general u *vojsci*. (He was a general in the army.)
6. On je dao dužnosti svojim *vojscama*. (He gave orders to his armies.)